{"text_id":37468,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," present"," a"," novel"," approach"," for"," performing"," spectral"," estimation"," on"," a"," sphere",","," which"," has"," numerous"," applications"," in"," ge","ophysics"," and"," cosmology","."," The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," for"," accurate"," character","izations"," of"," the"," underlying"," physical"," processes"," that"," occur"," on"," the"," surface"," of"," a"," sphere","."," Our"," approach"," uses"," tools"," from"," spherical"," harmonics"," analysis",","," which"," allow"," us"," to"," decompose"," the"," signal"," into"," different"," frequency"," components"," that"," can"," be"," analyzed"," separately","."," We"," apply"," our"," method"," to"," a"," variety"," of"," data"," sets",","," including"," temperature"," and"," gravitational"," potential"," maps"," of"," the"," cosmic"," microwave"," background"," radiation",","," and"," magnetic"," field"," measurements"," of"," the"," earth","'","s"," surface","."," ","\n","Our"," results"," show"," that"," our"," method"," out","performs"," existing"," techniques",","," particularly"," for"," data"," sets"," with"," a"," high"," degree"," of"," complexity","."," Specifically",","," we"," achieve"," higher"," resolution"," and"," more"," accurate"," estimates"," of"," the"," power"," spectrum"," of"," the"," data","."," One"," of"," the"," key"," benefits"," of"," our"," approach"," is"," that"," it"," is"," computationally"," efficient",","," with"," the"," ability"," to"," scale"," to"," large"," data"," sets","."," ","\n","Overall",","," our"," work"," attempts"," to"," solve"," the"," problem"," of"," accurately"," characterizing"," physical"," processes"," on"," a"," sphere",","," which"," has"," important"," implications"," for"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," scientific"," disciplines","."," The"," results"," of"," our"," study"," have"," the"," potential"," to"," lead"," to"," new"," insights"," into"," the"," structure"," and"," evolution"," of"," the"," universe"," and"," the"," earth","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}